{
  "newspaper_id": "lankadeepa-lk",
  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/latest_news/\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd-\u0db7\u0dd6\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca-\u0d87\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd6-\u0db6\u0dc0-\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1-\u0d8b\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9-\u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c-\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca-\u0dc3\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7/1-619329",
  "time_ut": 1662371686,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd \u0db7\u0dd6\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d87\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd6 \u0db6\u0dc0 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 \u0d8b\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A suspect with bullets said to have been fired from the struggle area",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the police, a person who came to hand over a magazine with 30 T-56 live bullets to the Panadura North Police, claiming that it was found in the Golfe Aragala area, has been arrested.",
        "A 35-year-old resident of Gorakana, Panadura was arrested after he came to the police station with a magazine containing bullets.",
        "It is said that the magazine is believed to belong to a firearm belonging to a member of the security forces who was on duty at the Golfe Agala area, and the suspect has given statements that it was found lying in the Agala area.",
        "However, a senior police officer said that investigations are being conducted regarding how the suspect got the magazine containing the bullets and whether he had committed any crime."
      ],
